      <title>花旗称对冲基金在英国预算公布前抛售英镑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/citi-says-hedge-funds-are-selling-the-pound-ahead-of-uk-budget-m2ok2dum</link>
