      <title>中国、印度开始从边境摩擦地区撤军</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/china-india-start-removing-troops-from-border-friction-points</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几天前，中印两国领导人举行会晤，随后两国军队开始从喜马拉雅山争议边界剩下的两个摩擦点撤军。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/china-india-start-removing-troops-from-border-friction-points</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 07:12:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默表示他愿意讨论英国过去的奴隶贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/starmer-says-he-s-open-to-talks-on-uk-s-historic-slave-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默表示，英国愿意与其他英联邦国家讨论其在奴隶贸易的历史参与，但不会提供赔偿。人们预计，本周在萨摩亚举行的领导人峰会将同意在联合公报中提及赔偿正义问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/starmer-says-he-s-open-to-talks-on-uk-s-historic-slave-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 03:45:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
